<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ق ي ض<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤١٥٨ - ق ي ض]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قاضَ يَقِيض، قِضْ، قَيْضًا، فهو قائِض، والمفعول مَقيض <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• قاض الشَّيءُ:</span> تشقَّق <span class="c1">"خشبٌ قائض"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• قاض الجِدَارُ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - تهدَّم وانهال <span class="c1">"قاضتِ الدُّورُ بسبب الزِّلزال"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢ - تصدَّع.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">• قاضه بالشَّيء:</span> عاضه عنه، وأبدله به <span class="c1">"قاضه السِّلعةَ الثَّمينةَ بلوحة فنّيّة"</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>